The platform documentation follows a hierarchical URL structure:
- `/analytics/` for core analytics features and charts
- `/feature-experiment/` for experimentation capabilities  
- `/data/` for CDP and data management features
- `/sdks/` for instrumentation documentation
- `/apis/` for API references
- `/admin/` for administrative functions
